	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://www.dealextreme.com/details.dx/sku.15852" class="postlink">SuperCard SD at DealExtreme</a>
<br />
<br />To save the SRAM to the SD card after you play, you have to do a <a href="http://wiki.pocketheaven.com/Supercard#QPC_Saving" class="postlink">quick power cycle</a>. Turning the GBA's power off for one second on a SuperCard acts like a long reset on a PowerPak.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


