		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Now we're <em>really</em> becoming Pocket Heaven.
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle">neilbaldwin wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">The BIOS dumper just shows a white screen and nothing is written to the SD card.</div><br />You have to patch the BIOS dumper with the SuperCard's driver. See the <a href="http://dldi.drunkencoders.com/index.php?title=Main_Page" class="postlink">DLDI Wiki</a>. See also <a href="http://wiki.pocketheaven.com/GBA_BIOS#libfat" class="postlink">instructions</a>.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">As for the patching (of PocketNES?) you described, I'm unsure what you're telling me I need to do?</div>
<br /><a href="http://wiki.pocketheaven.com/SupercardGBASlowdowns" class="postlink">PHWiki:SupercardGBASlowdowns</a>. Dwedit could probably tell you better than I.

		

